snippet.title: Street Fighter II - Full Walkthrough/No Commentary [Java Game]
snippet.description:
Street Fighter II it was a java game developed by CAPCOM Mobile and released in 2006

Is a classic fighter of 90-s. Choose any fighter and defeat your opponent applying different hits. The game offers high quality animation, combo hits and sound. You will surely feel nostalgic playing this game on slot machines!

Link to the game: https://phoneky.com/games/?s=download&id=j3j89779
